Package: bio3dview
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Visualization of Biomolecular Structure Data 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Barry", "Grant",
      email = "bjgrant@ucsd.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2215-4196")
    )
  )
Description: Generate attractive interactive molecular graphics from 'bio3d' 
  objects using minimal code. Major functions link 'bio3d' to the 'NGLVieweR' 
  package enabling the display of biomolecular structure analysis results in 
  the R console, in quarto/R Markdown documents, and in Shiny web applications.
